title: Screenshot Captor
description:
A freeware file saved as an .exe.

Program takes screenshots of the:
-entire workspace
-current screen
-active window
-selected region
-fixed size region
-windows object or scrolling window
-repeat last size+position

you can also use a timer

*this is freeware but when the program is started up, it will ask for a donation/key from giving a donation- if you have a key please notify me so i can post it here*
